I"B<p>Email subjects are not UTF-8 encoded, even if the Content Type is set to <code class="highlighter-rouge">Content-Type: text/plain; charset='utf-8'</code>.
To make the subject UTF-8 encoded, set the subject header line to:</p>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>Subject: =?utf-8?B?&lt;$BASE64_ENCODED_SUBJECT&gt;?=
</code></pre></div></div>

